title: AHSAA announces fall reclassification
description: Along with Friday’s historic announcement by the Alabama High School Athletic Association (AHSAA) concerning its separation of public and private schools in championship competition, was the announcement of the organization’s reclassification for the next athletic calendar, 2026-27.
